net.cloud.client.entity.player

Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.cloud.client.entity.Entity
      • net.cloud.client.entity.player.Player
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Bufferable

    public class Player
extends Entity
implements Bufferable
    The Player object. Home of the player. Holds the player's data. Keeps the player's data safe. A hub for all of the player's information. The root of the save data. Yes.
